headline: O’Reilly Automotive price target raised to $1,440 from $1,337 at Roth MKM
summary: Roth MKM raised the firm’s price target on O’Reilly Automotive (ORLY) to $1,440 from $1,337 and keeps a Buy rating on the shares. The company’s Q4 comps have re-accelerated and the firm remains constructive on the stock following in-line EPS and issuance of solid FY25 guidance despite the soft end market conditions, as O’Reilly utilizes its best in class business model to post accelerated growth, the analyst tells investors in a research note.
